Subtask: Find the supporting documents and answer for: Which band formed first, Sunrise Avenue or Marcy Playground?
Research history:
Step 1 tool call: [tool_call]search("Which band formed first, Sunrise Avenue or Marcy Playground?")[/tool_call]
Step 1 observation: {"results": [{"doc_id": "D06", "title": "Marcy Playground (album)", "hint": "Use read(\"D06\") to inspect this document."}, {"doc_id": "D05", "title": "Sunrise Avenue discography", "hint": "Use read(\"D05\") to inspect this document."}, {"doc_id": "D08", "title": "Sunrise Avenue", "hint": "Use read(\"D08\") to inspect this document."}, {"doc_id": "D00", "title": "Marcy Playground", "hint": "Use read(\"D00\") to inspect this document."}, {"doc_id": "D02", "title": "Sherry Fraser", "hint": "Use read(\"D02\") to inspect this document."}]}
